summary:
This is a savegame right at the beginning where the race menu is shown.
Savenumber is 1!
descriptionHtml:
Since I didn\'t found a clean save with savenumber 1 I will upload one.
Of course there is also a possibility to skip the intro with a mod but why using a extra mod for something you only need to do one time? :P

This savegame has a save counter of 1 so it is completely fresh.
I also didn\'t load any mod ESP so the savegame should be totally clean.

Installation

My Documents > My Games > Skyrim > Saves
author: AltDunmer
